---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Learn more about Murat Karslioglu. Background, experience, and interests."
>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-20 md:py-28">
    <h1
      class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-[var(--color-text-primary)] sm:text-5xl"
    >
      About
    </h1>

    <div class="mt-10 space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">
      <p>
        I'm Murat Karslioglu, a product leader and 3x startup founder
        specializing in storage systems and AI infrastructure. I currently
        work as a Staff Product Manager for Cloud Storage at Lambda, where I
        focus on building storage infrastructure for GPU compute and AI
        workloads.
      </p>
      <p>
        I've spent over a decade working across the storage stack, from
        distributed filesystems and object storage to cloud-native
        infrastructure and Kubernetes. Before Lambda, I led the Global Field
        Architects pre-sales team at MinIO. I hold a patent for modular
        interface-independent storage solutions.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16">
      <h2
        class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-[var(--color-text-primary)]"
      >
        Background
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">
        <p>
          I've founded three startups and worked at companies ranging from
          early-stage to enterprise scale. My career has been at the
          intersection of storage engineering and product strategy, building
          products across distributed storage, desktop virtualization, and
          cloud infrastructure.
        </p>
        <p>
          I'm the author of
          <em>Kubernetes in Production Best Practices</em> (Packt, 2021) and
          <em>Kubernetes: A Complete DevOps Cookbook</em> (Packt, 2020), and a
          frequent speaker at industry conferences on storage, Kubernetes,
          and cloud-native infrastructure.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16">
      <h2
        class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-[var(--color-text-primary)]"
      >
        Expertise
      </h2>
      <ul class="mt-6 grid gap-3 text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] sm:grid-cols-2">
        {
          [
            "Storage Systems & Architecture",
            "AI Infrastructure",
            "Cloud-Native & Kubernetes",
            "Distributed Systems",
            "Product Strategy & GTM",
            "Technical Writing & Patents",
          ].map((skill) => (
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-accent)]" />
              {skill}
            </li>
          ))
        }
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16">
      <a
        href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/muratkarslioglu/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--color-accent)] hover:underline"
      >
        Connect on LinkedIn &rarr;
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 border-t border-[var(--color-border)] pt-8">
      <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-tertiary)]">
        The views and opinions expressed on this site are my own and do not
        necessarily reflect the views, positions, or policies of my employer or
        any organization I am affiliated with. All content is provided for
        informational purposes only.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
